{"ID":270359, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"359\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs358.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs360.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 359<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">for there is no redemption for them<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> in this world nor in the world to come.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I could go back and trace every subject of interest concerning the relationship of man to God,\n  if I had time. I can enter into the mysteries; I can enter largely into the eternal worlds;<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> for Jesus\n  said, &ldquo;In my Father&rsquo;s house are many mansions; if it were not so, I would have told you. I go to\n  prepare a place for you&rdquo; (John 14:2).<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> Paul says, &ldquo;There is one glory of the sun, and another glory\n  of the moon, and another glory of the stars; for one star differeth from another star in glory. So also\n  is the resurrection of the dead&rdquo; (1 Cor. 15:41).<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> What have we to console us in relation to the dead?<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span>\n  We have reason to have the greatest hope and consolations for our dead of any people on the earth;\n  for we have seen them walk worthily<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> in our midst, and seen them sink asleep in the arms of Jesus;<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span>\n  and those who have died in the faith<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> are now in the celestial kingdom of God.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> And hence is the\n  glory of the sun.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Righteous Mourners Rejoice<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">You mourners have occasion to rejoice, speaking of the death of Elder King Follett; for your\n  husband and father is gone to wait until the resurrection of the dead<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span>&mdash;until the perfection of the\n  remainder; for at the resurrection your friend will rise in perfect felicity<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> and go to celestial glory,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span>\n  while many must wait myriads of years before they can receive the like blessings; and your\n  expectations and hopes are far above what man can conceive;<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> for why has God revealed it to us?<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I am authorized to say, by the authority of the Holy Ghost,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> that you have no occasion to fear;\n  for he is gone to the home of the just.<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> Don&rsquo;t mourn, don&rsquo;t weep.<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> I know it by the testimony of the\n  Holy Ghost<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> that is within me; and you may wait for your friends to come forth to meet you in the\n  morn of the celestial world.<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Rejoice, O Israel!<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> Your friends who have been murdered for the truth&rsquo;s sake<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> in the\n  persecutions<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> shall triumph gloriously<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> in the celestial world, while their murderers shall welter<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span>\n  for ages in torment, even until they shall have paid the uttermost farthing.<span class=\"footRef\">26<\/span> I say this for the benefit\n  of strangers.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I have a father, brothers,<span class=\"footRef\">27<\/span> children, and friends who have gone to a world of spirits.<span class=\"footRef\">28<\/span> They are\n  only absent for a moment. They are in the spirit, and we shall soon meet again. The time<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111640\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111640)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111640)\">Mosiah 16:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111888\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111888)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111888)\">Alma 11:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111913\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111913)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111913)\">Alma 12:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112968\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112968)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112968)\">Moro. 7:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107972\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107972)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107972)\">Matt. 12:31-32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113737\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113737)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113737)\">D&amp;C 42:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114424\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114424)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114424)\">D&amp;C 76:34<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114695\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114695)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114695)\">D&amp;C 84:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116401\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116401)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116401)\">D&amp;C 132:27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111765\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111765)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111765)\">Alma 3:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112163\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112163)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112163)\">Alma 34:34<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114476\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114476)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114476)\">D&amp;C 76:86<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116447\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116447)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116447)\">D&amp;C 132:55,63<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108791\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108791)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108791)\">John 14:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109606\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109606)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109606)\">1 Cor. 15:41<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112386\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112386)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112386)\">Alma 56:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109890\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109890)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109890)\">Col. 1:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113396\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113396)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113396)\">D&amp;C 20:69<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109582\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109582)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109582)\">1 Cor. 15:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112781\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this